title: Converse Rubber Tracks - disCOVERed: Alexandra Stewart covers "Black Water"
description:
Fashion and music are constantly reinvented when artists pay homage by "covering" classic pieces. So, for Fashion's Night Out 2012, Converse commissioned new interpretations of classic songs.

"Black Water" was written by Patrick Simmons and made famous by the Doobie Brothers. Alexandra Stewart gave this classic song a modern makeover when she visited Converse Rubber Tracks studio to record her dreamy arrangement.

"BLACK WATER"
WRITTEN BY PATRICK SIMMONS
